org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world

Interface Node

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Documentable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ApplicationNode, ExternalNode
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ApplicationNodeImpl, ExternalNodeImpl, NodeImpl

    public interface Node
extends Documentable
    A representation of the model object 'Node'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Host Name
    • Endpoints
    • Deployments

    See Also:
    WorldPackage.getNode()
